WEBVTT

00:00:57.803 --> 00:01:00.682
And maybe, especially,
people sort of like me,

00:01:00.706 --> 00:01:03.284
self-described progressive,

00:01:03.308 --> 00:01:05.048
don't want to be racist.

00:01:05.883 --> 00:01:07.365
Good white people.

00:01:07.818 --> 00:01:09.091
(Laughter)

00:01:09.115 --> 00:01:11.022
Any good white people in the room?

00:01:11.046 --> 00:01:12.125
(Laughter)

00:01:12.149 --> 00:01:15.708
I was raised to be that sort of person.

00:01:15.732 --> 00:01:18.200
I was a little kid in the '60s and '70s,

00:01:18.224 --> 00:01:21.059
and to give you some sense of my parents:

00:01:21.083 --> 00:01:23.701
actual public opinion polls at the time

00:01:23.725 --> 00:01:28.642
showed that only a small minority,
about 20 percent of white Americans,

00:01:28.666 --> 00:01:31.026
approved and supported